<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 09:06:42 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a53591eceed9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一家名为Replay Toys的新玩具和流行文化商店刚刚在梅肯开业，于是我顺道去参观了其丰富的收藏品。逛这家店很有趣。我不确定这类大型雕像的市场有多大，因为它们售价高达数百美元，但不可否认它们很酷。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A life-size statue of the Predator from the Predator films crouches on a tree branch inside a pop culture store. The alien hunter wears detailed metallic armor over its reptilian skin, with black dreadlock-like tendrils, shoulder-mounted plasma cannon, and an open mandible revealing sharp fangs. The display is posed mid-hunt against a jungle-themed base, with shelves of masks and collectibles visible in the background." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a53591eceed9.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 09:06:42 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5358eb133d6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一家名为Replay Toys的新玩具和流行文化商店刚刚在梅肯开业，于是我顺道去参观了其丰富的收藏品。逛这家店很有趣。我不确定这类大型雕像的市场有多大，因为它们售价高达数百美元，但不可否认它们很酷。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A detailed bust of Pennywise the Dancing Clown from IT is displayed inside a glass case. The sinister clown has a pale white face with glowing yellow eyes, bright red hair, a red nose, and a wide grin revealing sharp teeth. He wears a weathered gray Victorian-style costume with a large ruffled collar and red pom-poms, leaning forward with an intense, menacing stare." height="3711" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a5358eb133d6.jpg" width="2783"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 09:05:50 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a53587909f94</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一家名为Replay Toys的新玩具和流行文化商店刚刚在梅肯开业，于是我顺道去参观了其丰富的收藏品。逛这家店很有趣。我不确定这类大型雕像的市场有多大，因为它们售价高达数百美元，但不可否认它们很酷。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A life-size display of Leatherface from The Texas Chain Saw Massacre stands inside a pop culture store, wearing a pale pink shirt, black tie, and stained yellow butcher's apron. The character raises a large mallet over one shoulder while reaching forward with the other hand, wearing a stitched flesh-colored mask with messy dark hair and an open-mouthed grin. Shelves of collectibles and store displays fill the background." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a53587909f94.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 09:04:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a53581c228be</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一家名为Replay Toys的新玩具和流行文化商店刚刚在梅肯开业，于是我顺道去参观了其丰富的收藏品。逛这家店很有趣。我不确定这类大型雕像的市场有多大，因为它们售价高达数百美元，但不可否认它们很酷。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A statue of a green turtle with a red mask and sais stands in a toy store. Shelves filled with colorful toys are in the background." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a53581c228be.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 09:02:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5357f5dcf70</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一家名为Replay Toys的新玩具和流行文化商店刚刚在梅肯开业，于是我顺道去参观了其丰富的收藏品。逛这家店很有趣。我不确定这类大型雕像的市场有多大，因为它们售价高达数百美元，但不可否认它们很酷。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Life-size Deadpool statue in a comic store, holding up a finger with katanas on his back. A colorful display of comics and posters is in the background." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" sr